Package io.github.zero88.jooqx.datatype

Interface UserTypeAsJooqType<V,J>

Type Parameters:
V - Vert.x SQL data type
J - The jOOQ data type and a user type - i.e. any type available from SQLDataType
All Superinterfaces:
BridgeConverter<J,J>, org.jooq.ContextConverter<J,J>, org.jooq.Converter<J,J>, ConverterRepr<J,J>, DataTypeMapper<V,J,J>, Serializable
public interface UserTypeAsJooqType<V,J> extends DataTypeMapper<V,J,J>
It is short form of DataTypeMapper that means a record field is used user type as jOOQ data type
See Also:
  • DataTypeMapper
  • Converter
API Note:
In nutshell, it is equals with default JooqxConverter
